{
  "stem": "10162.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we-- we just lived-- another thing for the Jews who went back to their homeland, which was Stalinist Russian satellite countries, Soviet satellite countries, was an added thing, because you went home, and you were not allowed to talk about what you went through.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was almost-- it was like they made you ashamed of what you went through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you would say something that-- well, in my case, when I went back and I saw what's happening, at one point I wanted to go out-- go back to Germany to the American-- this American camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I got as far as Slovakia, and they put me into a camp because I was Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, suddenly I was Hungarian there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they let me out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went back to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I saw I cannot go further than that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I was working in Budapest under communism, somebody reported me, which was the order of the day-- everybody reported everybody else anonymously.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You never found out who said why and, you know, just-- terrible things happened-- that I-- I was going to leave.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I left the country for imperialist states.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, we had to write autobiographies all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they compared one thing to the other, where you had to say not just who you are, where were you born, but what was your mother and your grandmother and great grandfathers' profession.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were digging what was your origin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you weren't from working class or maybe peasant class, then you-- plenty trouble.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I didn't put this in my autobiography, that I one time went out as far as Slovakia and turned to right back like a week later.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somebody reported me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so just-- so anyway, I use that when there was a trial.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a party trial.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, I was standing there like, I don't know, like Dreyfus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, well, it's because, you know, I-- I was a young girl, and I came back alone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw there was no one there, and I thought I'll go back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they started to holler at me, what, you trying to make people feel sorry for you?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know-- just I realized you weren't allowed to even say that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're going to stop the tape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
